								<div class="options">
									<blockquote><small>Options</small></blockquote>
									<form>
										<div class="form-group">
											<label for="pattern-editor-option-nb-repetitions">Loop <i>n</i> times</label>
											<input type="number" class="form-control"
												id="pattern-editor-option-nb-repetitions" placeholder="1" min="1" />
											<span class="help-block">
												You can optionally chain several times the structure to form
												your pattern's complete rhythmic structure.
												<br />
												<b>Ex :</b> <i>1</i> (the default) means "don't loop several times"
